data.description: Welcome to the beautiful gated Deer Spring subdivision located in the award-winning Piedmont School district. This home features 4 bedrooms and 2 1/2 bathrooms, 2 living areas, and a large corner lot with a 6 ft privacy fence. A split floor plan with the primary bedroom and bathroom on one side of the house and the other three bedrooms and full bath on the opposite side makes this a great space for a large family. The spotless kitchen features stainless steel appliances,3cm granite, custom cabinets, a large pantry, and a breakfast bar that opens to the dining room. The large master features a master bath with 2 walk-in closets, a garden tub, and a separate shower. Security and safety features include an In-ground tornado shelter, tornado straps, and anchor bolts, a fire suppression system, and a generator transfer switch for backup power. This gated community includes a neighborhood pool and cabana for its residents.
